{"id":416868,"date":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":13}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"上海民歌选辑","genre":"","count":"62","ytitle":"","mtitle":"总路线在我心中","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走路直腰挺胸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志气赛过长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想红似太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话响如洪钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——总路线在我心中，中国纺织机械厂"}]}